author: ehillenius
msg: - WizardModel is now available for steps (breaks clients that did override init(model), replace with onInit(model))
- IFormValidator instances can now be added to the WizardStep, which will transparently pass them on to the form, while making sure
the validators for a certain step are only executed when that step is the currently active one.
